OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1773165971
OL,3,CDurham Cricket cancel mens' tour of
OL,4,CAbu Dhabi as Middle East tensions
OL,5,Ccontinue
OL,7,FDurham Cricket have announced they
OL,8,Fhave cancelled their pre-season tour
OL,9,Fof Abu Dhabi due to ongoing tensions
OL,10,Fin the Middle East.
OL,12,FThe club were due to fly to the United
OL,13,FArab Emirates on Monday 9 March, but
OL,14,Ffollowing discussions have agreed "the
OL,15,Fbest course of action" is to not
OL,16,Ftravel.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
