PN,42902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1773165971
OL,3,CDurham Cricket cancel mens' tour of
OL,4,CAbu Dhabi as Middle East tensions
OL,5,Ccontinue
OL,7,FThe announcement comes following days
OL,8,Fof further missile and drone attacks
OL,9,Fin the region, with Israeli forces
OL,10,Ftargeting Iranian leadership and
OL,11,Fsecurity forces, the IDF said on
OL,12,FWednesday.
OL,14,FIn a statement, the club's Director of
OL,15,FCricket, Marcus North said: "The
OL,16,Fsafety and wellbeing of our players
OL,17,Fand staff is always our absolute
OL,18,Fpriority.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1773165971
OL,3,CDurham Cricket cancel mens' tour of
OL,4,CAbu Dhabi as Middle East tensions
OL,5,Ccontinue
OL,7,F"We have been monitoring the situation
OL,8,Fclosely alongside the relevant
OL,9,Fauthorities and, after careful
OL,10,Fconsideration, we believe this is the
OL,11,Fright decision.
OL,13,F"While it's disappointing not to
OL,14,Ftravel, we are already working on
OL,15,Falternative plans to ensure the squad
OL,16,Fis fully ready for the start of the
OL,17,Fseason."
OL,19,FHe added the thoughts of the club are
OL,20,Fwith everyone affected by the conflict
OL,21,Fin the region.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/4
